            "value": "啟用 EXTREME MODE 將解除所有限制器:\n• Delay: ALL DISABLED（瀏覽·DL·收藏）\n• Download: NO SPEED LIMIT\n• Connections: 6 → 20 parallel\n• Prefetch: ±1 → ±5 pages\n• Gallery Preview: FULL IMAGE PRELOAD\n• OCR Batch: 3 → 6 parallel\n• URL Cache: EXPIRY CHECK DISABLED\n\n⚠️ BAN RISK. 重啟自動關閉。"
