    "WebP: 変換せず CGImageSource で逐次 decode。Boomerang 対応、ストレージ節約。\nMP4: HEVC MP4 に事前変換、AVPlayer で安定ループ。HDR は AVVideoComposition で全域適用。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WebP: No conversion, sequential decode via CGImageSource. Boomerang supported, saves storage.\nMP4: Pre-converted to HEVC MP4, stable looping via AVPlayer. HDR applied globally via AVVideoComposition."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WebP: 不转换，通过 CGImageSource 逐帧解码。支持 Boomerang，节省存储。\nMP4: 预转换为 HEVC MP4，AVPlayer 稳定循环。HDR 通过 AVVideoComposition 全局应用。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WebP: 不轉換，透過 CGImageSource 逐 frame 解碼。支援 Boomerang，節省儲存。\nMP4: 預轉換為 HEVC MP4，AVPlayer 穩定循環。HDR 透過 AVVideoComposition 全域套用。"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WebP: 변환 없이 CGImageSource 로 순차 디코드. Boomerang 지원, 저장 공간 절약.\nMP4: HEVC MP4 로 사전 변환, AVPlayer 로 안정 루프. HDR 은 AVVideoComposition 으로 전역 적용."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WebP: Keine Konvertierung, sequenzielle Dekodierung über CGImageSource. Boomerang-Unterstützung, spart Speicher.\nMP4: Vorkonvertierung zu HEVC MP4, stabile Schleife über AVPlayer. HDR global über AVVideoComposition."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WebP : pas de conversion, décodage séquentiel via CGImageSource. Boomerang pris en charge, économie de stockage.\nMP4 : pré-converti en HEVC MP4, boucle stable via AVPlayer. HDR appliqué globalement via AVVideoComposition."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WebP: sin conversión, decodificación secuencial vía CGImageSource. Boomerang compatible, ahorra almacenamiento.\nMP4: preconvertido a HEVC MP4, bucle estable vía AVPlayer. HDR aplicado globalmente vía AVVideoComposition."
          }
        }
      }
    },
